                    <head>Scope and Contents Note</head>
                    <p>The boxes consist of chapter revisions and drafts, including corresponce between the author and publisher regarding the book chapters. The chapters consist of document compilations regarding the relief efforts in Belgium during and after World War II as associated to George Gay.</p>
